Package: mbDecoda
Type: Package
Title: A Debiased Approach to Compositional Data Analysis for Microbiome Surveys
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Yuxuan",
           family = "Zong",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "zongyuxuan@sjtu.edu.cn")
Description: The mbDecoda package provides a debiased approach to compositional data analysis specifically designed for microbiome surveys. The methods implemented in this package are aimed at detecting differentially abundant taxa between different populations while adjusting for confounding variables and controlling the false discovery rate (FDR).
